POETS Client side tool chain description:

Compile a libthrift.jab file by entering your thrift folder and go to /lib/java. run the ant script.
copy the libtrhrift.jar to /java/poetsio/lib/.

After this, enter /java/poetsio/ and run 

# ant dist

to generate the poetsio.jar library. This will also generate the thrift classes for java. The poetsio.jar library will also contain the libthrift.jar. 
